// Test group: performance parameters
// Test purpose: region delay
//
// Test description:
// Region delay is the time elapsed from note-on till the region plays.
//
// This test has several regions with same sample and a different
// delay and transpose for each.
// Play a key and observe my enormous scoring skills.
// verify that each note dies in the polyphony counter.

